I think Lucifer gave Mazikeen authority over the his gates, so she just used the gate to hop up to Heaven, or as close as she could get.  The main gate definitely seems settable -- usually we've seen it go to his world, but the Titans wanted to use it for Heaven, and he sent them to Effrul instead. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#FFFF99>- </font><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/blucifer>Lucifer</a><font color=#FFFF99> - </font><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fluciferfrm1>Lucifer</a> <font color=#FFFF99> - </font><a href="http://lightbringer.mattpeckham.com/">Lightbringer: The Unofficial Lucifer Site</a><font color=#FFFF99> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.3e<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

